14:29:55.120 [INFO] - preserve the existing note body below the frontmatter as the source OCR or human-readable content
14:29:55.120 [INFO] - do not invent fields that are not supported by the visible note
14:29:55.120 [INFO] - if the visible invoice or bill data does not mention a currency, assume euros for `total_eur`, `unit_eur`, and `line_eur`

